{% comment %}
  About / Our Story — Intro (blue cloud blob + founders sign + Bihar caption).
  Self-contained: copy is literal, art is loaded from theme assets via asset_url.
{% endcomment %}

<section class="about-intro about-intro-{{ section.id }} color-{{ section.settings.color_scheme }}">
  <div class="about-intro__container">

    <div class="about-intro__top">
      <div class="about-intro__blob-wrapper">
        <img
          src="{{ 'about-blob.png' | asset_url }}"
          alt=""
          width="1200"
          height="710"
          loading="lazy"
          class="about-intro__blob-bg"
        >

        <div class="about-intro__sparkle about-intro__sparkle--left" aria-hidden="true">
          <img src="{{ 'about-spark.png' | asset_url }}" alt="" width="100" height="100" loading="lazy">
        </div>

        <div class="about-intro__blob-content">
          <p>We started The Boring Foods Company because we were deeply confused about health and wellness ourselves. Everywhere we looked, there was <strong>noise, misinformation</strong> and too many <strong>trends</strong> built on fear.</p>
          <p>The only tools we knew how to trust were the ones we&rsquo;d built our lives around: asking the kind of questions that most people skip, going beyond the surface, and getting deep, rich insights.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="about-intro__sparkle about-intro__sparkle--right" aria-hidden="true">
          <img src="{{ 'about-spark.png' | asset_url }}" alt="" width="100" height="100" loading="lazy">
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="about-intro__bottom">
      <div class="about-intro__sign-wrapper">
        <img
          src="{{ 'about-sign.png' | asset_url }}"
          alt="To Patna — a hand-drawn road sign"
          width="600"
          height="592"
          loading="lazy"
          class="about-intro__sign-image"
        >
      </div>

      <div class="about-intro__bottom-text-wrapper">
        <div class="about-intro__bottom-text">
          <p>It&rsquo;s how we met in 2019: two newly graduated 22-year-olds, freshly back from the US, working as economic development researchers in Bihar. That year taught us something important: <strong>if you want the real story, you have to go to the source.</strong></p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>

{% stylesheet %}
  .about-intro {
    background-color: #fbf3cc;
    padding: 60px 20px 0;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .about-intro__container {
    max-width: 1100px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    position: relative;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: stretch;
  }

  .about-intro__top {
    position: relative;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
  }

  .about-intro__blob-wrapper {
    position: relative;
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 40px auto 0;
    min-height: 400px;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    text-align: center;
    padding: 80px 60px;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .about-intro__blob-bg {
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: fill;
    z-index: 0;
  }

  .about-intro__blob-content {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
    color: #fbf3cc;
    font-family: var(--font-body--family, "Aesthet Nova", Georgia, serif);
    font-size: 20px;
    line-height: 1.4;
    max-width: 600px;
    text-align: left;
  }

  .about-intro__blob-content p {
    margin: 0 0 1em;
  }

  .about-intro__blob-content p:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  .about-intro__blob-content strong {
    font-weight: 800;
  }

  .about-intro__sparkle {
    position: absolute;
    width: 80px;
    height: auto;
    z-index: 2;
  }

  .about-intro__sparkle img {
    width: 100%;
    height: auto;
    display: block;
  }

  .about-intro__sparkle--left {
    left: -15px;
    top: 50%;
    transform: translateY(-50%);
  }

  .about-intro__sparkle--right {
    right: -20px;
    top: 50%;
    transform: translateY(-50%);
  }

  .about-intro__bottom {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    justify-content: space-between;
    gap: 0;
    margin-top: -40px;
    padding-right: 20px;
  }

  .about-intro__sign-wrapper {
    flex: 0 0 250px;
  }

  .about-intro__sign-image {
    width: auto;
    height: 13rem;
    display: block;
  }

  .about-intro__bottom-text-wrapper {
    flex: 1;
    padding-top: 40px;
  }

  .about-intro__bottom-text {
    font-family: var(--font-body--family, "Aesthet Nova", Georgia, serif);
    font-size: 20px;
    margin-top: 20px;
    line-height: 1.4;
    color: #5d57c5;
    padding-right: 90px;
  }

  .about-intro__bottom-text p {
    margin: 0;
  }

  .about-intro__bottom-text strong {
    color: #5d57c5;
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .about-intro {
      padding: 12px 12px 0;
    }

    .about-intro__container {
      max-width: 100%;
      overflow-x: hidden;
    }

    .about-intro__blob-wrapper {
      max-width: 100%;
      margin-top: 0;
      padding: 36px 20px;
      min-height: auto;
    }

    .about-intro__blob-bg {
      object-fit: cover;
    }

    .about-intro__blob-content {
      font-size: 14px;
      line-height: 1.3;
      text-align: center;
      max-width: 100%;
    }

    .about-intro__sparkle {
      display: none;
    }

    .about-intro__bottom {
      flex-direction: row;
      align-items: center;
      margin-top: 6px;
      padding-right: 0;
      gap: 16px;
      text-align: left;
    }

    .about-intro__sign-wrapper {
      flex: 0 0 auto;
      width: auto;
      max-width: 100px;
    }

    .about-intro__sign-image {
      height: auto;
      max-height: 140px;
      width: 100%;
    }

    .about-intro__bottom-text-wrapper {
      padding-top: 0;
      width: 100%;
    }

    .about-intro__bottom-text {
      font-size: 14px;
      line-height: 1.3;
      padding-right: 0;
      margin-top: 0;
      text-align: left;
    }
  }
{% endstylesheet %}

{% schema %}
{
  "name": "About Story Intro",
  "settings": [
    {
      "type": "color_scheme",
      "id": "color_scheme",
      "label": "Color scheme",
      "default": "scheme-1"
    }
  ],
  "presets": [
    { "name": "About Story Intro" }
  ]
}
{% endschema %}
